- [ ] Move DBML conversion logic
- [ ] Move schema combination functionality
- [ ] Add DBDocs integration

**Phase 5: Extract DB Package**
- [ ] Create packages/db
- [ ] Create database abstraction layer
- [ ] Integrate with adapters
- [ ] Move transaction management

**Phase 6: Integration & Testing**
- [ ] Update all imports and dependencies
